HEADWORD: Meacock
<hw>Mea"cock</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Prob. fr.
<ets>meek</ets> + <ets>cock</ets>.]</ety> <def>An uxorious, effeminate,
or spiritless man.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
